OL,3,CMan, 71, who stalked actress Anna
OL,4,CFriel bailed ahead of sentencing
OL,6,FA man from Berkshire, who stalked
OL,7,Factress Anna Friel for nearly three
OL,8,Fyears, has been bailed ahead of his
OL,9,Fsentencing next month.
OL,11,FPhil Appleton, 71, sent numerous
OL,12,Fmessages, visited the actress's home
OL,13,Faddress on several occasions and left
OL,14,F"unwanted" gifts between January 1
OL,15,F2022 and December 11 2024, Reading
OL,16,FCrown Court previously heard.
OL,18,FAppleton, of Windsor, pleaded guilty
OL,19,Fto a stalking offence under Section 2A
OL,20,Fof the Protection from Harassment Act
OL,21,F1997 earlier this week.
