OL,3,CMan, 71, who stalked actress Anna
OL,4,CFriel bailed ahead of sentencing
OL,6,FHe was due to be sentenced on
OL,7,FThursday, but judge Alan Blake
OL,8,Fadjourned the hearing until September
OL,9,F18 for a pre-sentence report to be
OL,10,Fcarried out.
OL,12,FThe defendant, who the court heard has
OL,13,Fbeen in custody for six months and has
OL,14,Fspent time in a mental health
OL,15,Ffacility, was granted conditional bail.
OL,17,FAppleton must not contact Friel or
OL,18,Fenter the Royal Borough of Windsor and
OL,19,FMaidenhead and is to co-operate with
OL,20,Fthose conducting the pre-sentence
OL,21,Freport.
